title: The Upturned Glass [1947 - UK] James Mason
description:
The Upturned Glass (1947 - UK)

Crime / Drama / Film-Noir

starring . . . . James Mason, Rosamund John, Pamela Mason
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0039947/


Prominent neurosurgeon Michael Joyce, who for reasons unexplored, tells a lecture room of students the story of his affair with a married woman and the details of her sudden death. Believing his lover was murdered, he shares with the audience how he plans to lure and murder the person he thinks was responsible.
